\n* [[2016 Massachusetts Senate elections]]<ref>{{cite web |accessdate= April 8, 2020 |work= Sec.state.ma.us |author= Commonwealth of Massachusetts, Elections Division |url= https://electionstats.state.ma.us/elections/search/year_from:2016/year_to:2016/office_id:9/stage:General |title= 2016 State Senate election }}</ref>\n* [[2018 Massachusetts Senate elections]]<ref>{{cite web |accessdate= April 8, 2020 |work= Sec.state.ma.us |author= Commonwealth of Massachusetts, Elections Division |url= https://electionstats.state.ma.us/elections/search/year_from:2018/year_to:2018/office_id:9/stage:General |title= 2018 State Senate election }}</ref>\n\n===Massachusetts House of Representatives===\n{{see also|List of Massachusetts General Courts}}\n* \u2026\n* [[2002 Massachusetts House of Representatives elections]]<ref>{{cite web |accessdate= April 8, 2020 |work= Sec.state.ma.us |author= Commonwealth of Massachusetts, Elections Division |url= https://electionstats.state.ma.us/elections/search/year_from:2002/year_to:2002/office_id:8/stage:General |title= 2002 State Representative election }}</ref>\n* [[2004 Massachusetts House of Representatives elections]]<ref>{{cite web |accessdate= April 8, 2020 |work= Sec.state.ma.us |author= Commonwealth of Massachusetts, Elections Division |url= https://electionstats.state.ma.us/elections/search/year_from:2004/year_to:2004/office_id:8/stage:General |title= 2004 State Representative election }}</ref>\n* [[2006 Massachusetts House of Representatives elections]]\n* [[2008 Massachusetts House of Representatives elections]]\n* [[2010 Massachusetts House of Representatives elections]]<ref>{{cite web |accessdate= April 8, 2020 |work= Sec.state.ma.us |author= Commonwealth of Massachusetts, Elections Division |url= https://electionstats.state.ma.us/elections/search/year_from:2010/year_to:2010/office_id:8/stage:General |title= 2010 State Representative election }}</ref>\n* [[2012 Massachusetts House of Representatives elections]]<ref>{{cite web |acc